{"tid":1527729,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉貼］詳細popo 策略分析","createTime":"2019-09-01T11:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T18:14:10.000Z","uid":83106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"57e0e396f7a5525dfcd5016d6c9ec9fb764f3466","tid":1527729,"uid":83106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T11:16:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>背景</strong><br />\n出入機場有陸路同機鐵<br />\n陸路又分人工島同東涌<br />\n出入東涌有黨鐵同巴士<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Popo 策略</strong><br />\n今日popo 嘅策略係困獸鬥<br />\n<br />\n第一步 - 折斷人流物流補及<br />\n<br />\n依一步分兩部分<br />\n先阻截最直接到機場方法： 機鐵<br />\n然後係青馬收費站廣場拖慢車流<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v48p3ey.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv48p3ey.png&h=3766a6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1點先出發嘅人流去到4點先過到橋<br />\n同時間分流旅客比佢哋搭機場快綫離開<br />\n<br />\n第二步 - 擺陣推機場巴士站前線到東涌<br />\n<br />\n由1點到4點 個3小時<br />\n防暴由機場開始推示威者到東涌橋<br />\n<br />\n第三步 - 圍城<br />\n<br />\n全面暫停所有鐵路<br />\n東涌變成孤島<br />\n同時重新開放經人工島離開嘅巴士比旅客離開<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KPkzF4s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKPkzF4s.png&h=a8c3f590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四步 - 收網<br />\n<br />\n東涌大圍捕<br />\n<br />\n策略成功之處在於分離到抵港旅行同示威者<br />\n任何時間仲有一個方法俾旅客離開<br />\n缺點在於犧牲左去機場旅客<br />\n<br />\n同時間東涌同人工島有一點唔同<br />\n就係人工島有少量遊客<br />\n但東涌就有其他交通<br />\n不過兩者都客易變成孤島<br />\n<br />\n利伸<br />\n圖片及文章轉貼自香港討論區及baby kingdom<br />\n本人唔鼓勵大家討論任何違犯禁制令嘅對策"},{"pid":"24ccfe56ccf6120fec5c847721e13f75e6dca2eb","tid":1527729,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼 6條命 900被捕 無數斷手斷腳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831黨鐵恐襲傷者消息全無</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n九二九三大三罷！<br />\n設死線 升級持續罷工<br />\n日日罷工 日日入機場<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVP4X9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVP4X9g.jpg&h=c7d56cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5iA4Pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4453ed6897b8fd769a1ff74583b5e9eb3d847060","tid":1527729,"uid":83106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b2e005750a914c158fa099cd9adba5e05cc44ca2","tid":1527729,"uid":300697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T18:14:10.000Z","msg":"多了個人工島，情況複雜了。"}]}